---
title: Venison Steak & Almond-Prosciutto Crumb with Pumpkin Gratin & Lemon-Feta Greens
description: Steak and veg is an all-time classic, but let’s add a couple of special twists! Indulge in glowing golden chicken with a nutty prosciutto crumb, paired with a creamy pumpkin gratin and lemony greens. This feast is fit for a king!

*We’ve replaced the half chicken in this recipe with venison steak due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
